  ## Moderate Crimes
  - The maximum sentence per Moderate Crime is 7 minutes
  - Moderate crimes involve more serious offenses that can disrupt station operations or endanger personnel, requiring stricter enforcement.
  <Table Columns="4">
    <ColorBox>
      <Box>
        Code
