    <ColorBox>
      <Box HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Margin="2">
        This covers criminal uses of force, with intent to seriously injure, but no intent to kill. That would be some variation of Murder. This law also constitutes unlawful mindbreaking.
